NumberExpression, Observable, Property<Number>, ReadOnlyProperty<Number>, ObservableLongValue, ObservableNumberValue, ObservableValue<Number>, WritableLongValue, WritableNumberValue, WritableValue<Number>, StyleableProperty<Number>
public class SimpleStyleableLongProperty
extends StyleableLongProperty
This class extends SimpleLongProperty and provides a full implementation of a StyleableProperty. This class is used to make a LongProperty, that would otherwise be implemented as a SimpleLongProperty, styleable by CSS.
Since:
JavaFX 8.0
See Also:
SimpleLongProperty, CssMetaData, StyleableProperty, StyleableLongProperty
